## List Services = Always Paginated (MANDATORY RULE)

> **أي endpoint بيرجع list → لازم يكون paginated.**

```dart
// ❌ FORBIDDEN — GET list without pagination (standalone screen)
class ProductsCubit extends AsyncCubit<List<ProductEntity>> { ... }

// ✅ CORRECT — paginated list
class ProductsCubit extends PaginatedCubit<ProductEntity> { ... }
```

### Exceptions — When AsyncCubit<List<T>> is OK:

| Case | Why |
|------|-----|
| Dropdown data (cities, categories) | Small fixed list, no scroll needed |
| Multi-section screen sub-lists (banners) | Short list within a larger screen |
| Filter chips / tags | Small, rarely exceeds 20 items |

